- content_for :title do
  Boss page for
  = @boss_token.gallery
  on IMGSHR

.content-header
  .row
    .text-center
      %h2
        Boss page for
        = link_to @boss_token.gallery, @boss_token.gallery, data: {no_turbolink: true}

.row
  .col-md-2
  .col-md-5
    %p
      Besides providing a gallery delete link (see on the right), this page
      refreshes your boss token cookie. It can be used to delete individual
      pictures, to make a gallery read only, and to enable or disable ratings.
  .col-md-3
    %p.text-right
      = link_to gallery_delete_path(@boss_token), method: :delete, class: 'btn btn-danger', data: { confirm: "Really delete #{@boss_token.gallery}?" } do
        = icon :delete
        Delete the whole gallery!
  .col-md-2

.row
  .text-center
    = image_tag gallery_delete_path(@boss_token, format: :svg), class: 'qr-code'
